2
00:00:48,020 --> 00:00:51,020
[Episode 13]

3
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:55,700
[Director's Office]

4
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:57,200
Mr. Gu,

5
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,320
Mr. Liu didn't name specifically

6
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,560
Gu Tongpei as the successor.

7
00:01:01,030 --> 00:01:02,920
Seems he's handing you an opening.

8
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,950
Why not seize it

9
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,000
and take the position?

10
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:09,230
But what they want is money.

11
00:01:11,430 --> 00:01:14,200
I'm making Gu Tongpei the successor

12
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,590
to make him let his guard down.

13
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:18,310
After all, the old man just died.

14
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:21,150
If I overthrew the successor he chose,

15
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,950
it'd be tough to convince the public.

16
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,560
Gu Tongpei is consumed
by vengeance.

17
00:01:27,150 --> 00:01:28,510
He'll accomplish nothing.

18
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:32,430
Later, when I step in
as emergency governor,

19
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,560
it makes my authority justifiable.

20
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,790
Your judgment is spot-on!

21
00:01:36,150 --> 00:01:37,040
Hurry up!

22
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,000
Take the gold from my safe

23
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,150
and distribute it to veteran officers.

24
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:42,120
My succession depends on their backing.

25
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,430
And rush

26
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:46,950
the search for Chu Minghui.

27
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,510
I need her alive.

28
00:01:48,510 --> 00:01:49,280
Yes.

29
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,710
Tongpei,

30
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,120
sorry for your loss.

31
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:38,000
You and Chu Minghui
killed Father together.

32
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,360
I'll absolutely uncover the truth.

33
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:42,240
None of you will escape.

34
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,240
You've misunderstood me,

35
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,910
Tongpei.

36
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,630
I was also deceived by her.

37
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,080
In the past,

38
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,960
I was such a fool.

39
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,630
Only after Father's death
did I truly see

40
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,680
you two are the ones

41
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,710
I hold dearest in this life.

42
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:11,360
From this day forward,

43
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,360
you're my only family

44
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,030
in this world.

45
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,030
Tongpei,

46
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:22,910
we must stand together.

47
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:25,680
Chu Minghui murdered Father

48
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,310
in such a brutal way.

49
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,310
We'll make her pay.

50
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:34,190
During his lifetime,

51
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:37,360
Father cherished you above all else.

52
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,030
You must

53
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:43,120
personally avenge him.

54
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,750
Otherwise, he'll never rest in peace.

55
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,720
Gu Tongpei,

56
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,920
go ahead and torment Chu Minghui.

57
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,120
This is all for Father.

58
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,950
Here you are.

59
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,190
Are you

60
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:47,040
sending a maid to stay here?

61
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,750
The lodging fees are charged per person.

62
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:58,950
Rest assured, I'll keep my lips sealed.

63
00:04:58,950 --> 00:04:59,830
Hurry inside now.

64
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,720
Wait here.

65
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:06,560
Yes.

66
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,070
All men

67
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,160
are scums.

68
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,160
Does it hurt?

69
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,160
My father must have been

70
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,600
in much more pain when he died.

71
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,000
Why did you kill him?

72
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,800
Why did you torture him

73
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,160
in such a cruel way?

74
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,720
Was this your own scheme,

75
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,720
or a plot hatched with Gu Tongce?

76
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,480
Spill it.

77
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:14,040
I want the whole truth.

78
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:18,950
If you're seeking revenge,
kill me.

79
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,920
The rich torture people

80
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,000
in a truly unique way.

81
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:32,630
Chilling just to hear about them.

82
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,560
Stay out of their spat.

83
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,630
Getting mixed up in this

84
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,750
will only bring you trouble.

85
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,040
Chu Minghui,

86
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:03,630
things won't end like this.

87
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:09,020
[Memorial Tablet for Gu Rongchong]

88
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,830
Bow before my father.

89
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:31,750
In your dreams!

90
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,830
Chu Minghui,

91
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,830
I gave you chance after chance,

92
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,790
yet you lied to me again and again,

93
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,320
trampling my sincerity under your feet!

94
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,120
You even murdered my father cruelly!

95
00:08:42,550 --> 00:08:44,720
I really wish I could cut you to pieces!

96
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,550
That was my father!

97
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,150
Even if he'd done something wrong,

98
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,000
he gave me life and raised me!

99
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:59,320
How could you kill him like that?

100
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:05,360
Just tell me why,

101
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,550
and I'll grant you a merciful death.

102
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,240
Nothing left to say.

103
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,550
I deceived you.

104
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:16,480
I owed you.

105
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:18,750
Now I repay you.

106
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:48,120
You may kill yourself,

107
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,240
but don't dirty
my father's memorial hall.

108
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,600
Now that you hate me this much,

109
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:18,240
why not finish me off?

110
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:24,320
Chu Minghui,

111
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,120
without my permission,

112
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,960
don't even think about dying.

113
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:31,240
Deal with the injury you caused.

114
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,700
♪Love is an abyss one cannot escape♪

115
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:52,060
♪The more I doubt, the more I fear♪

116
00:10:53,180 --> 00:10:55,420
♪Sparks of hatred
ignite within the heart♪

117
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,790
How could you hit her?

118
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:58,910
This is

119
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,120
my mother's necklace.

120
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:02,460
♪I guard myself over and over again♪

121
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,600
She left it to the one
I treasure most.

122
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:13,300
♪I hesitate in every word
and every moment♪

123
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:16,940
♪I feign, struggle♪

124
00:11:17,580 --> 00:11:20,460
♪Flee, and break♪

125
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:28,500
♪The endless shackle of darkness♪

126
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:36,700
♪Let love come♪

127
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:40,180
♪No more worries♪

128
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,000
As long as you're here,

129
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:44,840
even if I suffer grave injuries,

130
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,980
I'll surely heal quickly.

131
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:47,860
♪Crush it♪

132
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,750
From now on,

133
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,000
take good care of yourself.

134
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:51,940
♪Keep it to yourself♪

135
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,600
Never let yourself be hurt easily again.

136
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:03,100
♪Let the hatred go♪

137
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:06,480
You deceived me.

138
00:12:06,540 --> 00:12:09,540
♪Don't dwell♪

139
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:13,980
♪Only when flowers wither
will scars form♪

140
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:17,180
♪Let love and hate
scatter with the wind♪

141
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,000
Keep this in mind.

142
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,550
This is what you owe me.

143
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,390
Your life belongs to me.

144
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,150
Do you think my wounds and agony

145
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:25,630
can be mended easily?

146
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:29,060
♪Let myself be free♪

147
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,240
Miss Chu.

148
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:44,080
Keep an eye on her.

149
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,910
Don't let her die.

150
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:01,030
Miss Chu,

151
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:03,390
please don't go head-to-head with him.

152
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:05,480
Do you two have to be like this?

153
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,510
You're both such good people.

154
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:09,120
Don't torture each other.

155
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:13,080
I'm not a good person.

156
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,750
Perhaps only when I vanish,

157
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,120
can all this come to an end.

158
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:23,670
Miss Chu,

159
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:26,670
I don't know what happened

160
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,550
between you two.

161
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:29,960
But only by staying alive,

162
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,320
can you resolve misunderstandings.

163
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:35,910
Yet resolving them

164
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,480
would thrust him deeper into anguish.

165
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:44,150
If he knows our feud,

166
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,790
it'll bring him endless torment.

167
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:06,420
Die,

168
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:08,740
I'd like some hot noodle soup.

169
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:10,820
Could you make me a bowl?

170
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:12,420
Sure.

171
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:13,700
Just leave it here.

172
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:16,620
Go and return soon.

173
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:28,420
Die.

174
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,420
Sir.

175
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,940
Keep her wounds dry

176
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:35,660
these two days.

177
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:38,100
Be vigilant!

178
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:39,820
Ensure that she won't get a fever.

179
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:41,140
Understood.

180
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,380
Sir,

181
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:46,620
please stop torturing each other.

182
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:58,660
Go prepare some nourishing food for her.

183
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,660
Yes.

184
